    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pork has browned, reduce the heat to medium-high, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>shallot</strong> and cook for a further 2-3 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> with your <strong>fennel</strong> <strong>seeds</strong> and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1682435582826-x200.jpg",
