    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the ragu has thickened, stir through the <strong>drained tortiglioni </strong>with a splash of <strong>starchy pasta water</strong>, a knob of <strong>butter </strong>and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>pork, fennel & red wine ragu with tortiglioni</strong></p>",
